title: Govinda Restaurante Vegetariano
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Indian, Delivery, Take-out, Hare Krishna
description: Operated by Hare Krishna followers. All food is vegan consisting of a rotating daily menu that includes includes juice, soup, main dish, dessert, and tea. Affiliated health food store on corner. The only non-vegan item is honey which is offered as a sweetener for drinks.
